string_view?

Followed the upstream way of handling the path.

AFAIU, ztring_view is the same as string_view, but just that with the former it is guaranteed to have null termination.

William has a commit in stdplus repo, that introduces this type. https://github.com/openbmc/stdplus/commit/61a81bc814aa51b6aaf7ada8dc4285597e0061f3

William, if there's something more on this, can you please add it here?
